The paper discusses the training of convolution neural networks (CNN) for unstable CNN accelerators, which involves integrating uncertain circuit behaviors into the CNN models through additional accelerator-specific training. This topic falls under the intersection of several computer science sub-fields, including computer architecture (cs.AR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), control systems (cs.SY), and embedded systems (cs.ET). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
